(100mm Circle Profile - 18mm Deep)
(Feed: 2000mm/min  Spindle: 18000 RPM)
(Pass depth: 4mm  Passes: 5  [4/8/12/16/18mm])
(Tool start: X50 Y0 - edge of circle, center at X0 Y0)
G21          (metric)
G90          (absolute)
G17          (XY plane)
M3 S18000    (spindle on CW 18000 RPM)
G0 Z5        (safe height)
G0 X50 Y0    (rapid to start point)

(Pass 1 - Z-4mm)
G1 Z-4 F500
G2 X50 Y0 I-50 J0 F2000

(Pass 2 - Z-8mm)
G1 Z-8 F500
G2 X50 Y0 I-50 J0 F2000

(Pass 3 - Z-12mm)
G1 Z-12 F500
G2 X50 Y0 I-50 J0 F2000

(Pass 4 - Z-16mm)
G1 Z-16 F500
G2 X50 Y0 I-50 J0 F2000

(Pass 5 - Z-18mm final)
G1 Z-18 F500
G2 X50 Y0 I-50 J0 F2000

G0 Z5        (retract)
G0 X0 Y0     (return to origin)
M5           (spindle off)
M30          (end of program)
